OL,3,CConcerns online content is causing
OL,4,Cextreme behaviour in island's children
OL,6,FAn online safety event has revealed
OL,7,Fthe shocking impact internet trends
OL,8,Fhave on children's behaviour in Jersey.
OL,10,FAt a meeting at Victoria College,
OL,11,Fparents were shown examples of bad
OL,12,Fbehaviour that included children
OL,13,Fsharing explicit images on social
OL,14,Fmedia groups and making threats of a
OL,15,Fsexual nature.
OL,17,FOne child even threw themselves from a
OL,18,Fmoving car when their device was taken
OL,19,Faway, with another boy asking whether
OL,20,Fit was normal to choke women.
