OL,3,CConcerns online content is causing
OL,4,Cextreme behaviour in island's children
OL,6,FThe revelations have proved so
OL,7,Fshocking, that one parent is now
OL,8,Fwriting to Jersey's Education
OL,9,FMinister, Deputy Rob Ward, to share
OL,10,Fconcerns about the use of smartphones
OL,11,Famong young children.
OL,13,FVicky O'Neil told ITV News: "It was
OL,14,Fsobering to go to the event and hear
OL,15,Fthe things they were talking about and
OL,16,FI really think there is a safeguarding
OL,17,Fcrisis that we are just not
OL,18,Facknowledging as a community.
