OL,3,CConcerns online content is causing
OL,4,Cextreme behaviour in island's children
OL,6,F"It's really concerning as a parent
OL,7,Fthat we're just blindly letting
OL,8,Fchildren have access to social media
OL,9,Fand phones from such a young age. I
OL,10,Fthink they're exposed to things that
OL,11,Feven adults shouldn't be exposed to,
OL,12,Fit's a gateway to the wild west and
OL,13,Fthere's no controls of what they can
OL,14,Fsee and what they can be involved
OL,15,Fwith."
OL,17,F97% of children have a smartphone by
OL,18,Fthe age of 12, according to Ofcom.
