OL,4,Cextreme behaviour in island's children
OL,6,FFellow parent and author Douglas
OL,7,FKruger has extensively researched the
OL,8,Fpsychology concerning online addiction.
OL,10,FHe said: "Perhaps one of the most
OL,11,Fconcerning things is that the devices
OL,12,Flearn our behaviour, so it's not just
OL,13,Fthat the device is addictive, it's
OL,14,Falso that the device becomes more
OL,15,Faddictive over time. It learns what
OL,16,Fthe child enjoys and provides more of
OL,17,Fit.
