OL,6,F"One small element of hope is that the
OL,7,Fmind is infinitely malleable. It
OL,8,Fgrows, it changes, it morphs - but it
OL,9,Fdoes so less after the age of 24. You
OL,10,Fcan recover the neuro damage done by
OL,11,Fthese screens, but first, you have to
OL,12,Fstop damaging them.
OL,14,F"You can tell the difference from one
OL,15,Fday to the next if a child has been
OL,16,Fplaying for hours on a screen or
OL,17,Fplaying outside."
