OL,6,FJersey's Children, Young People,
OL,7,FEducation and Skills department said:
OL,8,F"Through the PSHE curriculum, students
OL,9,Fwill learn about developing healthy
OL,10,Finterpersonal relationships both on
OL,11,Fand offline.
OL,13,F"This includes dealing with risky and
OL,14,Fnegative behaviour, all forms of
OL,15,Fbullying, including the distinct
OL,16,Fchallenges posed by online bullying,
OL,17,Fsexual and other violence, and online
OL,18,Fencounters.
